## Summary
This documentation page explains how to create, edit, and manage dashboards in Amplitude, allowing users to collect related charts in a single view. It covers features like adding charts and cohorts, designating official dashboards, filtering, commenting, subscribing to dashboard reports, and creating dashboard templates for reuse.

